<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>中国新闻|今日突发新闻|路透社</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/</link><description>Reuters.com 是您获取最新中国新闻故事和时事的在线来源，确保我们的读者及时了解任何突发新闻动态 - RSSHub 用爱制作(https://github.com/DIYgod/RSSHub)</description><lastBuildDate>Thu, 25 Apr 2024 00:54:47 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>日元在 155 水平挣扎，市场对干预持谨慎态度</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/currencies/markets-wary-intervention-yen-struggles-155-level-2024-04-25/</link><description>周四，随着日本央行 (BOJ) 开始为期两天的利率制定会议，日元兑美元汇率被固定在 155 美元兑 155 美元的弱势区间，这让交易员担心东京方面是否会在政策审议仍在进行时进行干预。</description><pubDate>Thu, 25 Apr 2024 00:43:25 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/currencies/markets-wary-intervention-yen-struggles-155-level-2024-04-25/</guid></item><item><title>布林肯将在上海会见企业，开启艰难的中国之行</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/blinken-meet-businesses-shanghai-he-kicks-off-tough-china-trip-2024-04-25/</link><description>随着华盛顿和北京之间的关系趋于稳定，美国国务卿安东尼·布林肯将于周四在上海会见商界领袖，推动解决一系列威胁竞争对手之间新达成的平衡的问题。</description><pubDate>Thu, 25 Apr 2024 00:26:08 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/blinken-meet-businesses-shanghai-he-kicks-off-tough-china-trip-2024-04-25/</guid></item><item><title>焦点：中国比亚迪寻求重新定义电动汽车一代的奢华</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/chinas-byd-seeks-redefine-luxury-ev-generation-2024-04-24/</link><description>中国电动汽车制造商比亚迪将于周四在北京车展上展示其高端品牌的首款轿车，以向德国梅赛德斯-奔驰等公司发起挑战，后者三年前因销售缓慢而退出该品牌的开发。</description><pubDate>Wed, 24 Apr 2024 22:04:03 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/chinas-byd-seeks-redefine-luxury-ev-generation-2024-04-24/</guid></item><item><title>早盘竞价：日本外汇未出现，Meta 暴跌</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/global-markets-view-asia-graphic-pix-2024-04-24/</link><description>展望未来一天的亚洲市场。</description><pubDate>Wed, 24 Apr 2024 21:47:26 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/global-markets-view-asia-graphic-pix-2024-04-24/</guid></item><item><title>中国学生因威胁民主活动人士而在美国被判入狱</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/chinese-student-gets-us-prison-term-threatening-pro-democracy-activist-2024-04-24/</link><description>周三，一名中国音乐学生在美国监狱被判处九个月监禁，罪名是骚扰一名在波士顿伯克利音乐学院张贴支持中国民主传单的活动人士，并威胁要向中国执法部门举报她的活动。</description><pubDate>Wed, 24 Apr 2024 18:44:13 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/chinese-student-gets-us-prison-term-threatening-pro-democracy-activist-2024-04-24/</guid></item><item><title>拜登连任竞选不会停止使用 TikTok</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/us/bidens-re-election-campaign-wont-stop-using-tiktok-2024-04-24/</link><description>周三，一位竞选官员表示，乔·拜登的连任竞选活动计划继续使用 TikTok，此前不久，美国总统签署了一项法案，如果该应用程序的中国所有者未能剥离该应用程序，该法案将禁止该应用程序。</description><pubDate>Wed, 24 Apr 2024 17:23:53 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/us/bidens-re-election-campaign-wont-stop-using-tiktok-2024-04-24/</guid></item><item><title>受中国市场推动，意大利 Moncler 第一季度销售额增长 16%</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/retail-consumer/sales-italys-moncler-up-16-first-quarter-boosted-by-china-2024-04-24/</link><description>意大利时尚集团 Moncler 周三公布，按固定汇率计算，第一季度销售额增长 16%，这得益于中国强劲的需求，中国已成为一些奢侈品牌的痛处。</description><pubDate>Wed, 24 Apr 2024 16:00:38 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/retail-consumer/sales-italys-moncler-up-16-first-quarter-boosted-by-china-2024-04-24/</guid></item><item><title>中国缓慢复苏给奢侈品行业前景蒙上阴影</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/retail-consumer/luxury-sector-outlook-clouded-by-chinas-slow-recovery-2024-04-24/</link><description>欧洲大型奢侈品牌的最新销售数据并不能让人相信中国对高端时尚的需求正在复苏，这给该行业的前景蒙上了一层阴影。</description><pubDate>Wed, 24 Apr 2024 15:54:20 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/retail-consumer/luxury-sector-outlook-clouded-by-chinas-slow-recovery-2024-04-24/</guid></item><item><title>TikTok首席执行官预计将击败美国禁令：“我们哪儿也不去”</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/technology/tiktok-ceo-expects-defeat-us-restrictions-we-arent-going-anywhere-2024-04-24/</link><description>TikTok 首席执行官周三表示，该社交媒体公司预计将赢得一项法律挑战，以阻止总统乔·拜登签署的立法，他表示该法案将禁止 1.7 亿美国人使用其受欢迎的短视频应用程序。</description><pubDate>Wed, 24 Apr 2024 15:23:39 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/technology/tiktok-ceo-expects-defeat-us-restrictions-we-arent-going-anywhere-2024-04-24/</guid></item><item><title>由于欧盟的担忧，TikTok 暂停了新应用程序的奖励计划</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/technology/tiktok-suspend-tiktok-lites-reward-programme-amid-eu-concerns-2024-04-24/</link><description>周三，该公司在 X 社交媒体平台上表示，TikTok 将自愿暂停其新应用程序 TikTok Lite 的奖励计划，同时试图解决欧盟的担忧。</description><pubDate>Wed, 24 Apr 2024 15:05:09 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/technology/tiktok-suspend-tiktok-lites-reward-programme-amid-eu-concerns-2024-04-24/</guid></item><item><title>德国间谍机构警告企业不要对中国过于“天真”</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/europe/german-spy-agency-warns-companies-against-being-too-naive-china-2024-04-24/</link><description>德国国内间谍机构周三告诉企业，他们应该警惕北京的工业间谍活动，警告他们不要天真或过度依赖中国。</description><pubDate>Wed, 24 Apr 2024 14:37:52 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/europe/german-spy-agency-warns-companies-against-being-too-naive-china-2024-04-24/</guid></item><item><title>智利取代阿根廷成为 2025 年田径世锦赛主办国</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/sports/cycling/chile-replace-argentina-2025-track-world-championships-hosts-2024-04-24/</link><description>国际自行车联盟（UCI）周三表示，2025 年场地自行车世界锦标赛将在智利圣地亚哥举行，而不是之前宣布的在阿根廷圣胡安举行。</description><pubDate>Wed, 24 Apr 2024 14:31:47 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/sports/cycling/chile-replace-argentina-2025-track-world-championships-hosts-2024-04-24/</guid></item><item><title>ASML首席执行官表示美国限制维修部分中国设备不会影响盈利</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/technology/asml-ceo-says-us-restricts-servicing-some-china-equipment-wont-hurt-earnings-2024-04-24/</link><description>顶级半导体设备供应商ASML即将卸任的首席执行官周三表示，美国政府将阻止该公司在某些情况下对此前出售给中国客户的部分机器进行维修。</description><pubDate>Wed, 24 Apr 2024 14:08:29 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/technology/asml-ceo-says-us-restricts-servicing-some-china-equipment-wont-hurt-earnings-2024-04-24/</guid></item><item><title>汇丰银行表示，中国财富的增长推动了客户在美国的投资</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/finance/hsbc-says-growing-chinese-wealth-fuels-client-investments-us-2024-04-24/</link><description>汇丰银行美国和美洲区首席执行官迈克尔·罗伯茨表示，汇丰银行在中国和香港的富裕客户仍然渴望在美国投资。</description><pubDate>Wed, 24 Apr 2024 14:03:45 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/finance/hsbc-says-growing-chinese-wealth-fuels-client-investments-us-2024-04-24/</guid></item><item><title>科威尔期待水手队晋级亚洲冠军联赛决赛</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/sports/soccer/popp-hero-10-man-marinos-advance-asian-champions-league-final-2024-04-24/</link><description>哈里·科威尔周三带领日本横滨水手队通过点球大战战胜韩国蔚山现代队，首次进入亚洲冠军联赛决赛，他的目标是创造横滨水手队的历史。</description><pubDate>Wed, 24 Apr 2024 13:29:17 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/sports/soccer/popp-hero-10-man-marinos-advance-asian-champions-league-final-2024-04-24/</guid></item></channel></rss>